name: Fresh Discover Beauty Online
tag_list: beauty, skincare, makeup, cosmetics, perfume, fragrances, haircare
overview:
Fresh Fragrances and Cosmetics launched in Australia in 2004, and quickly acquired a large beauty presence. Fresh Fragrances and Cosmetics’ powerful beauty presence in the digital retail beauty industry is attributed to its unparalleled assortment of prestige beauty products, its commitment to excellence in quality and customer service, and to its well trained and dedicated employees. Fresh Fragrances and Cosmetics features an ever-increasing amount of classic and emerging brands across a broad range of product categories including skincare, makeup, fragrance, body care, hair care and beauty accessories. Fresh is committed to providing the ultimate in luxury and superior quality products, advice and customer care.

Luxury Brands

Fresh offers 600 of the world’s leading designer brand cosmetics including Chanel, Chloe, Clinique, DIOR, Estee Lauder, Giorgio Armani, Givenchy, Gucci Hermes, Lancome, Marc Jacobs, NARS, Tom Ford and Yves Saint Laurent, and over 20,000 products from cult classics to the latest in beauty releases.

Luxury Advice

Our mission is to help you look and feel your best. To do that, we offer the best of the best in global beauty and inspire customers with a fabulous mix of beauty news, the latest in beauty trends, expert beauty tips and tricks, a selection of creative gifts and unrivalled beauty advice. Fresh provides the ultimate beauty experience, and customers can enjoy an effortless and convenient shopping experience.

Our expert beauty advisors are here to help you:

Find the perfect foundation, lipstick, mascara, blusher that’s right for YOU
Find a skincare regime that targets your skin concerns
Update your makeup wardrobe
Choose the new season’s must have
Refresh your perfume collection

Luxury Care

Our dedicated customer care team is available to assist you with all of your needs. From discovering Fresh, checkout to delivery, to post-sale care, Fresh customers can enjoy an effortless and convenient shopping experience.

Our customer care team is available to assist you with:

Product shade selections
Detailed product information
Find an alternative for a discontinued product
Delivery questions
Exchange and return queries
Placing orders
Discovering beauty online
